Overview (4)

Date of Birth

23 March
1952, Wichita Falls, Texas, USA 


Birth NameRex Wayne Tillerson

Nickname
T-Rex    
Height

5' 10" (1.78 m)    


Mini Bio (1)


          Rex Tillerson was born on March 23, 1952 in Wichita Falls, Texas, USA as Rex Wayne Tillerson. He has been married to Renda St. Clair since June 21, 1986. They have four children.



Spouse (1)


               Renda St. Clair          

(21 June 1986            - 
present) (4 children)          



Trivia (5)

      Is an Eagle Scout and serves on the Boy Scouts of America's National Executive Board.


      Graduated from the University of Texas at Austin, in Austin, Texas in 1975 with a Bachelor of Science degree in civil engineering.


      Is the Chief Executive Officer (CEO) and a chairman of ExxonMobil Corporation.


      Has twin boys with his first wife.


      Secretary of State under President Trump.[April 2017].







